<div id="main_content">
	<h2>UCF Arena Holds First Commencement Ceremonies (With Video)</h2>
	
	<p class="article_info">
		
			By Zenaida Gonzalez Kotala and Chad Binette
		
		<span class="date">Updated Dec. 15, 2007</span></p>
	
	
	
		<div class="article_img" style="width: 261px;">

			<img alt="Article Main Picture" src="../resources/sites/UCF/content/live/NEWS/1000/NE1269/en_US/kisscrop.jpg" height="196" width="261"  /> 
			
				<p class="photo_credit">Photo: Jacque Brund</p>
			
			<p>A graduate receives a congratulatory kiss after she participated in the first commencement ceremony in the new UCF Arena.</p>
			
				<p class="note"><a class="full_photo" id="popup.jsp?article_id=00240041045494c8d01161d3164c1006592">Full Photo</a></p>
			
			
			
			
					
						
						
							
